{
  "texts": [
    "Chatbots have the option to continue a chat or start a new chat.",
    "Continuing a chat helps the chatbots stay on the same topic and respond accordingly.",
    "Since there were different subject areas in this data collection process, each prompt was started as a new chat to prevent related output.",
    "The prompts entered into both chatbots are as follows:",
    "• \"I am a 7 th grade math teacher."
  ]
}